{
  "stem": "21310.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had the bucket, actually more.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We have three buckets.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I-- I was pumping the water and giving the women the bucket.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were going around along the train and filling up these little cups, you know, that they-- some people had.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I remember just looking like, over my shoulder every so often, you know, to see if I glimpse somebody that-- that I knew.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And yet, I was scared that they might recognize-- somebody might recognize me and yell out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so-- and one time I also saved-- one woman, she was brought into the office.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the guy there, one of these German people, said-- I don't know who brought her in, if it was a Polish-- Polish railroad man or who.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But this one German railroad man said he had to call the [NON-ENGLISH] or the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he couldn't get through.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then he said, you call.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he walked out, and he walked out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And she was sitting there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I recognized she was Jewish, although she wouldn't admit it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But, you know, I knew that she was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And she was just terrified.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "She was sitting there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But there was nobody in the office but me and her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I told her, go, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she looks up, and I say, go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so she went, and I even told her a street where I knew she could maybe hide.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because there was some-- some little-- like a little forest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, go to your right and then-- and go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then the German, the railroad man came in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- well, maybe 15 minutes later.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he says, what happened?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Did you call?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said, well I don't know, that I had to go to the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
